# Fylrook

Fylrook is a **lightweight desktop utility** that helps you take control of messy folders, scattered files, and confusing filenames — all in just a few clicks.  

Whether you’re a student, developer, designer, or everyday PC user, Fylrook saves time by **organizing, renaming, and managing files intelligently**.

---

## 🚀 Key Features

### 📂 Smart File Organization
Automatically organize files by type, size, extension, or custom rules.

### ✏️ Batch File Renaming
Rename hundreds of files at once using prefixes, numbering, dates, and more.

### 🔗 File Shortcuts & URL Paths
Create quick access shortcuts and save useful file or web links.

### 📝 Built-in Notes
Attach notes to files or folders to remember important details.

### 🔒 File Hiding & Password Protection
Keep sensitive files private and secure.

### ⚡ Fast & Lightweight
No heavy background usage. Simple, clean, and efficient.

